State of Connecticut v. Dean Milligan (11106)

Daly, Foti and Landau, Js.

Argued October 27 decision released November 17, 1992 John C. Levanti, for the appellant (defendant). Jack W. Fischer, deputy assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were C. Robert Satti, Sr., state’s attorney, and Geoffrey Marion, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
